		<title>萬國通路微風信義店開幕！全新店裝亮相、開幕慶優惠同步登場</title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/10/20/%e8%90%ac%e5%9c%8b%e9%80%9a%e8%b7%af%e5%be%ae%e9%a2%a8%e4%bf%a1%e7%be%a9%e5%ba%97%e9%96%8b%e5%b9%95%ef%bc%81%e5%85%a8%e6%96%b0%e5%ba%97%e8%a3%9d%e4%ba%ae%e7%9b%b8%e3%80%81%e9%96%8b%e5%b9%95%e6%85%b6/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[火報]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Mon, 20 Oct 2025 07:12:06 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[公益]]></category>
